But here's something that will make your mouth water. Bacon cheese fries!!! And it's mozzarella. Great staff too. Always friendly and helpful.  Cons: if you're strapped for time then order by phone. Just know that they there's a minimum dollar amount. There isn't much in the way of parking spots. But if your okay with a bit of walking then your good.
